From: Nicolin Chen <b42378@freescale.com>
Date: Thu, 13 Jun 2013 19:51:04 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0210/1072] ARM: imx_v6_v7_defconfig: Enable imx-wm8962 by
 default

Commit 42914fdde5bcda9f9118f20456d2c22300cda645 upstream.

Enable imx-wm8962 and PM_RUNTIME, essential for WM8962 CODEC driver.

Signed-off-by: Nicolin Chen <b42378@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Shawn Guo <shawn.guo@linaro.org>
Signed-off-by: Shawn Guo <shawn.guo@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Hongbo Zhong <hongbo.zhong@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig |    2 ++
 1 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
index cc58452..581ef54 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
@@ -49,6 +49,7 @@ CONFIG_CMDLINE="noinitrd console=ttymxc0,115200"
 CONFIG_VFP=y
 CONFIG_NEON=y
 CONFIG_BINFMT_MISC=m
+CONFIG_PM_RUNTIME=y
 CONFIG_PM_DEBUG=y
 CONFIG_PM_TEST_SUSPEND=y
 CONFIG_NET=y
@@ -187,6 +188,7 @@ CONFIG_SND_SOC=y
 CONFIG_SND_IMX_SOC=y
 CONFIG_SND_SOC_PHYCORE_AC97=y
 CONFIG_SND_SOC_EUKREA_TLV320=y
+CONFIG_SND_SOC_IMX_WM8962=y
 CONFIG_SND_SOC_IMX_SGTL5000=y
 CONFIG_SND_SOC_IMX_MC13783=y
 CONFIG_USB=y
